  "description": "<i>Puzzle Time</i> is a puzzle game containing Crossword, Sudoku, Code Cruncher, Number Trail, and Anagram. Crossword, Sudoku, and Anagram are the well known puzzles, with stylus control. Code Cruncher looks like a crossword, but all the answers have been replaced by numbers. Number Trail shows a series of mathematical operations, and asks you the answer.<br><br>There are two modes. In Puzzle Time Mode, you need to successfully complete a certain number of puzzles within the allotted time, at which time you gain an award and move on to the next level. You can select which puzzles you are fond of, and which you dislike, changing how often they appear. In Free Play Mode, you can play any type of puzzle, with no time limit.",
